BEGIN:VTODO
UID:aisplanner-47@ais-new-student-planner
DUE;VALUE=DATE:20261018
SUMMARY:First Week To-Do
DESCRIPTION:- Get a calendar with important dates from your home school\, and add those dates to your plans in this calendar.\n- Add travel plans: add any family trips or personal plans to your plans in this calendar.\n- Try it yourself: tap any day on your calendar and add something personal — homework\, an extracurricular\, or anything else on your mind.\n- Add your Colegia email to your smartphone.\n- Add Teams to your smartphone and computer. Say hello to your teacher while there.\n- Change your Colegia password.\n- Review Colegia information. If you have questions\, rewatch the video from class.\n- Bookmark Help Desk. Save the AIS Dual Diploma Help Desk to your bookmarks.\n- Take the pre-test in each course so you can start working. You must do the pre-test to unlock the lessons.
CATEGORIES:AIS Planner,First Week To-Do
COLOR:chocolate
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
END:VTODO
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:aisplanner-48@ais-new-student-planner
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261018
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261019
SUMMARY:Complete First Week To-Do Items
DESCRIPTION:Complete First Week To-Do Items\n\n- Get a calendar with important dates from your home school\, and add those dates to your plans in this calendar.\n- Add travel plans: add any family trips or personal plans to your plans in this calendar.\n- Try it yourself: tap any day on your calendar and add something personal — homework\, an extracurricular\, or anything else on your mind.\n- Add your Colegia email to your smartphone.\n- Add Teams to your smartphone and computer. Say hello to your teacher while there.\n- Change your Colegia password.\n- Review Colegia information. If you have questions\, rewatch the video from class.\n- Bookmark Help Desk. Save the AIS Dual Diploma Help Desk to your bookmarks.\n- Take the pre-test in each course so you can start working. You must do the pre-test to unlock the lessons.\n\nCheck items off in your planner: https://jillmalman.github.io/ais-new-student-planner/
CATEGORIES:AIS Planner,First Week To-Do
COLOR:chocolate
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
