DESCRIPTION:- Check this calendar daily.\n- Check your Colegia email daily.\n- Stay organized: assignments are due every Sunday in each course. Use your pacing guides as checklists.\n- Log in to Cosmos regularly to check your grades.\n- Review teacher feedback on completed lessons.\n- Name your files properly and save them in the correct folder.\n- Prepare for live sessions when traveling — read the travel guide if you'll be away.
